#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:109
msgid "Show PHP errors and warnings on the frontend for administrators only. Useful for debugging issues on your site."
msgstr "Show PHP errors and warnings on the frontend for administrators only. Useful for debugging issues on your site."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:113
msgid "Remove WordPress version information from your site's HTML source code. This improves security by hiding which version you're using."
msgstr "Remove WordPress version information from your site's HTML source code. This improves security by hiding which version you're using."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:117
msgid "Remove WordPress emoji scripts and styles to reduce HTTP requests and improve page loading speed."
msgstr "Remove WordPress emoji scripts and styles to reduce HTTP requests and improve page loading speed."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:121
msgid "Limit REST API access to authenticated users only. Prevents unauthorized access to your site's data through the API."
msgstr "Limit REST API access to authenticated users only. Prevents unauthorized access to your site's data through the API."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:125
msgid "Completely disable XML-RPC to prevent DDoS attacks, brute force attempts, and other security vulnerabilities."
msgstr "Completely disable XML-RPC to prevent DDoS attacks, brute force attempts, and other security vulnerabilities."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:129
msgid "Limit the number of post revisions stored in the database to 5 per post. Reduces database size and improves performance."
msgstr "Limit the number of post revisions stored in the database to 5 per post. Reduces database size and improves performance."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:133
msgid "Disable comments globally on your site. Reduces spam, improves security, and reduces database load."
msgstr "Disable comments globally on your site. Reduces spam, improves security, and reduces database load."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:137
msgid "Disable WordPress Heartbeat API to reduce server load and improve performance, especially on shared hosting."
msgstr "Disable WordPress Heartbeat API to reduce server load and improve performance, especially on shared hosting."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:141
msgid "Remove unnecessary meta tags, links, and scripts from the WordPress head section. Reduces page size and improves loading speed."
msgstr "Remove unnecessary meta tags, links, and scripts from the WordPress head section. Reduces page size and improves loading speed."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:145
msgid "Disable WordPress oEmbed scripts to prevent external sites from embedding your content and improve loading performance."
msgstr "Disable WordPress oEmbed scripts to prevent external sites from embedding your content and improve loading performance."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:149
msgid "Automatically removes post revisions older than 45 days on a monthly schedule. Also optimizes database tables and cleans up transients."
msgstr "Automatically removes post revisions older than 45 days on a monthly schedule. Also optimizes database tables and cleans up transients."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:153
msgid "Add security headers like X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, and X-XSS-Protection to improve site security."
msgstr "Add security headers like X-Content-Type-Options, X-Frame-Options, and X-XSS-Protection to improve site security."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:157
msgid "Hide the WordPress admin bar on the frontend for all users except administrators. Provides a cleaner browsing experience for visitors."
msgstr "Hide the WordPress admin bar on the frontend for all users except administrators. Provides a cleaner browsing experience for visitors."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:161
msgid "Move jQuery and jQuery Migrate scripts from the header to the footer. Improves page loading speed by deferring JavaScript execution."
msgstr "Move jQuery and jQuery Migrate scripts from the header to the footer. Improves page loading speed by deferring JavaScript execution."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:165
msgid "Remove jQuery Migrate script to reduce file size and improve performance. Only enable if your theme and plugins don't require it."
msgstr "Remove jQuery Migrate script to reduce file size and improve performance. Only enable if your theme and plugins don't require it."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:169
msgid "Google Search Console verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Google Search Console verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:173
msgid "Yandex.Webmaster verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Yandex.Webmaster verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:177
msgid "Bing Webmaster Tools verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Bing Webmaster Tools verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:181
msgid "Baidu Webmaster Tools verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Baidu Webmaster Tools verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:185
msgid "Alexa verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Alexa verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:189
msgid "Pinterest verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Pinterest verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:193
msgid "Facebook Domain Verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""
msgstr "Facebook Domain Verification code (meta tag). Format: content=\"verification_code\""

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:197
msgid "Remove unnecessary SVG filters and Global Styles added by WordPress to reduce page size and improve loading performance."
msgstr "Remove unnecessary SVG filters and Global Styles added by WordPress to reduce page size and improve loading performance."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:201
msgid "Prevent author enumeration scans by redirecting requests like /?author=1 to homepage. Improves security by hiding author usernames."
msgstr "Prevent author enumeration scans by redirecting requests like /?author=1 to homepage. Improves security by hiding author usernames."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:205
msgid "Enable safe SVG upload support. Allows uploading SVG files with security sanitization to prevent XSS attacks."
msgstr "Enable safe SVG upload support. Allows uploading SVG files with security sanitization to prevent XSS attacks."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:209
msgid "Add preconnect and dns-prefetch hints for Google Fonts domains to improve loading performance and reduce connection time."
msgstr "Add preconnect and dns-prefetch hints for Google Fonts domains to improve loading performance and reduce connection time."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:213
msgid "Disable the file editor in WordPress admin to prevent unauthorized code modifications. This prevents users from editing theme and plugin files through the admin interface."
msgstr "Disable the file editor in WordPress admin to prevent unauthorized code modifications. This prevents users from editing theme and plugin files through the admin interface."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:217
msgid "Require email confirmation when administrators change their email address. Adds an extra layer of security to prevent unauthorized email changes."
msgstr "Require email confirmation when administrators change their email address. Adds an extra layer of security to prevent unauthorized email changes."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:221
msgid "Disable Dashicons CSS loading on the frontend for non-logged-in users. Reduces page size and improves loading speed."
msgstr "Disable Dashicons CSS loading on the frontend for non-logged-in users. Reduces page size and improves loading speed."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:225
msgid "Disable self-pingbacks (trackbacks from your own site). Reduces spam and unnecessary database entries."
msgstr "Disable self-pingbacks (trackbacks from your own site). Reduces spam and unnecessary database entries."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:229
msgid "Remove the 'Website' field from comment forms. Reduces spam and simplifies the commenting process."
msgstr "Remove the 'Website' field from comment forms. Reduces spam and simplifies the commenting process."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:233
msgid "Hide specific login error messages. Instead of 'Invalid username' or 'Incorrect password', shows a generic error message for security."
msgstr "Hide specific login error messages. Instead of 'Invalid username' or 'Incorrect password', shows a generic error message for security."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:237
msgid "Disable generation of unnecessary image sizes (thumbnail, medium, large, etc.) to save disk space and improve performance."
msgstr "Disable generation of unnecessary image sizes (thumbnail, medium, large, etc.) to save disk space and improve performance."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:241
msgid "Disable attachment pages and redirect media file URLs directly to the file itself. Improves SEO and user experience."
msgstr "Disable attachment pages and redirect media file URLs directly to the file itself. Improves SEO and user experience."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:245
msgid "Automatically empty trash every 7 days instead of the default 30 days. Reduces database size and improves performance."
msgstr "Automatically empty trash every 7 days instead of the default 30 days. Reduces database size and improves performance."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:249
msgid "Disable WooCommerce styles and scripts on non-shop pages. Improves loading speed on pages without WooCommerce functionality."
msgstr "Disable WooCommerce styles and scripts on non-shop pages. Improves loading speed on pages without WooCommerce functionality."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:253
msgid "Enable maintenance mode with a simple message for visitors. Administrators can still access the site normally."
msgstr "Enable maintenance mode with a simple message for visitors. Administrators can still access the site normally."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:257
msgid "Force SSL/HTTPS on all pages. Redirects all HTTP requests to HTTPS for improved security and SEO."
msgstr "Force SSL/HTTPS on all pages. Redirects all HTTP requests to HTTPS for improved security and SEO."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:261
msgid "Enable classic widgets editor instead of block-based widgets. Restores the traditional WordPress widgets interface."
msgstr "Enable classic widgets editor instead of block-based widgets. Restores the traditional WordPress widgets interface."

#: includes/Admin/Settings.php:265
msgid "Enable post cloning feature. Adds a 'Clone' link in the admin for posts, pages, and custom post types to create duplicates."
msgstr "Enable post cloning feature. Adds a 'Clone' link in the admin for posts, pages, and custom post types to create duplicates."

